1023
01:24:16,765 --> 01:24:20,360
- How about a dinner meeting?
- Wow. OK.

1024
01:24:20,469 --> 01:24:23,632
Next Friday. Bridges Restaurant.
Seven o'clock sharp.

1025
01:24:25,074 --> 01:24:27,167
I'll be there.

1026
