Mrs Doubtfire. You just have to.

1097
01:28:49,371 --> 01:28:51,896
Who could resist that little face?

1098
01:28:53,375 --> 01:28:55,900
- I promise.
- Thank you!

1099
01:28:57,179 --> 01:28:59,113
Thank you, dear.

1100
01:28:59,982 --> 01:29:01,847
- Are you all right?
- Fine.

1101
01:29:01,950 --> 01:29:04,009
Let's see... Nothing.

1102
01:29:04,119 --> 01:29:06,314
- Anything in May?
- Not a thing.

1103
01:29:06,388 --> 01:29:08,447
It doesn't look good.

1104
01:29:09,224 --> 01:29:12,785
I'm sorry. Mr Lundy is completely booked
for the next two months.

1105
01:29:13,228 --> 01:29:17,062
