- Sorry. There's nothing I can do.

1106
01:29:17,166 --> 01:29:20,067
Please. I can't cancel.
It's a huge opportunity.

1107
01:29:20,169 --> 01:29:23,332
Take my advice: don't cancel.

1108
01:29:26,608 --> 01:29:28,872
Thank you.

1109
01:29:43,358 --> 01:29:46,418
- Come along, Nattie.
- Hello, darling!

1110
01:29:46,862 --> 01:29:49,854
- Shouldn't you cover your shoulders?
- No! I'm fine.

1111
01:29:50,032 --> 01:29:52,432
- Good evening, Mr Lundy.
- Good evening.

1112
01:29:52,501 --> 01:29:56,369
Oh, God. Here we go.

1113
01:29:56,438 --> 01:29:59,168
- Mrs Doubtfire, you look wonderful.
- Thank you.

1114
01:29:59,241 --> 01:30:01,300
Come on. I hope you're all hungry.

1115
01:30:06,281 --> 01:30:09,444
- Good evening, Mr Lundy.
