1117
01:30:12,488 --> 01:30:15,286
But we can seat you.
Smoking or non-smoking?

1118
01:30:15,390 --> 01:30:17,881
Non-smoking, please.

1119
01:30:17,993 --> 01:30:21,986
- Tanya will seat you. Table 15.
