1120
01:30:23,098 --> 01:30:26,192
- Reservation. Dunmeyer.
- Yes, sir.

1121
01:30:26,869 --> 01:30:29,030
- Smoking or non-smoking?
- Non-smoking.

1122
01:30:29,104 --> 01:30:32,005
