- Mrs Doubtfire?

1131
01:31:13,248 --> 01:31:17,582
- Would you like to join us?
- Oh. I thought I saw Clint Eastwood.

1132
01:31:17,686 --> 01:31:21,349
That would make my day!
He is such a stud-muffin.

1133
01:31:21,456 --> 01:31:24,516
Will you excuse me, dear?
I have to check my wrap.

1134
01:31:24,593 --> 01:31:28,290
