1150
01:32:40,202 --> 01:32:42,261
- Isn’t it gorgeous!
- Is it real?

1151
01:32:42,371 --> 01:32:44,430
It is very real, Mrs Doubtfire.

1152
01:32:44,539 --> 01:32:49,670
